      * Perform brief initial investigation of the problem.
      * Attempt to resolve the problem.
      * Obtain hardware/software support if required.
      * Track problem when turned over to hardware/software support.
      * Verify with customer that service is restored after corrective
          action has been taken.
      * Enforce technical escalations.
      * Open tickets for Preventive Maintenance.
      * Perform special monitoring services for BT North America support 
          groups.
      * Make managerial escalations within the various support groups as
          required to guarantee quality of service provided to the
          customer.
